OL,3,CWoman who wrote book on grief after
OL,4,Chusband's death found guilty of his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FA woman who published a children's
OL,8,Fbook about coping with grief after her
OL,9,Fhusband died has been found guilty of
OL,10,Fhis murder.
OL,12,FKouri Richins was convicted of
OL,13,Fpoisoning her husband with fentanyl
OL,14,Fand found guilty of forgery and
OL,15,Ffraudulently claiming insurance
OL,16,Fbenefits after his death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
