OL,3,CWoman who wrote book on grief after
OL,4,Chusband's death found guilty of his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FRichins was also convicted of
OL,8,Fattempted murder for trying to poison
OL,9,Fher husband weeks earlier on
OL,10,FValentine's Day with a fentanyl-laced
OL,11,Fsandwich that made him black out.
OL,13,FThe internet search history from
OL,14,FRichins' phone included "what is a
OL,15,Flethal.dose.of.fetanayl," "luxury
OL,16,Fprisons for the rich America" and "if
OL,17,Fsomeone is poisned what does it go
OL,18,Fdown on the death certificate as," a
OL,19,Fdigital forensic analyst testified.
