OL,3,CWoman who wrote book on grief after
OL,4,Chusband's death found guilty of his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FProsecutors said Richins, 35, slipped
OL,8,Ffive times the lethal dose of fentanyl
OL,9,Finto a cocktail she gave her husband,
OL,10,FEric Richins, in March 2022 at their
OL,11,Fhome.
OL,13,FThey said she was $4.5 million in debt
OL,14,Fand believed she would inherit her
OL,15,Fhusband's estate worth more than $4
OL,16,Fmillion.
OL,18,FIn the months after her husband's
OL,19,Fdeath, Richins self-published a
OL,20,Fchildren's book Are You with Me? about
OL,21,Fcoping with the loss of a parent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
