OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe prosecution said Richins, an
OL,13,Festate agent, had found herself deeply
OL,14,Fin debt and was planning a future with
OL,15,Fanother man.
OL,17,FShe had opened numerous life insurance
OL,18,Fpolicies on her husband without his
OL,19,Fknowledge, with benefits totaling
OL,20,Fabout $2 million, prosecutors said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
