OL,3,CWoman who wrote book on grief after
OL,4,Chusband's death found guilty of his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"She wanted to leave Eric Richins but
OL,8,Fdid not want to leave his money,"
OL,9,FSummit County prosecutor Brad
OL,10,FBloodworth said.
OL,12,FSummit County Sheriff's detective Jeff
OL,13,FO'Driscoll said shortly after Richins'
OL,14,Farrest, her mother sent the book to
OL,15,Fthe sheriff's office in an anonymous
OL,16,Fpackage with a note saying it
OL,17,Fexemplified the "true Kouri, a devoted
OL,18,Fwife and adoring mother".
